title: DDFP 385: Week 1 Red Challenge Flag Picks
itunes:title: DDFP 385: Week 1 Red Challenge Flag Picks
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and Elliot Harrison as they make their Week 1 "Red Challenge Flag Picks." Shek also sits down with Willie McGinest and Nate Burleson to discuss what it takes to win a Super Bowl in the NFL.
